text: Foral Democratic Union (, UDF) was an electoral alliance in Navarre, formed by the People's Democratic Party (PDP), the Liberal Party and the Foral Democratic Party ahead of the 1987 Navarrese regional election. It merged into the Navarrese People's Union (UPN) in 1991. ==References== Category:Political parties in Navarre Category:Political parties established in 1987 Category:Political parties disestablished in 1991 Category:Defunct political party alliances in Spain
